<p>town. We are camped in huts here but expect to move off this afternoon 28.7.16</p>
<p>Gen. Birdwood visited camp this afternoon. We shifted camp and marched until 2 a.m. The distance was 14 miles to La Vicogne. We moved out of billets at 10 a.m. and marched 6 &frac12; miles to Bonneville 29.7.16</p>
<p>Marched to Halloy about 4 miles 30.7.16</p>
<p>Shifted back to La Vicogne today and expect to move off again tomorrow 9.8.16</p>
<p>Marched to Toutencourt</p>
